definitions.definition: A sovereign state with dominant status on the globe and a very advanced military , especially the United States or formerly the Soviet Union .
An extraordinary physical or mental ability, especially possessed by a superhero or supervillain .
Electricity generated in a large plant that is tied into a regional network, on a larger scale than was common in the early years of commercial electricity production.

main_definition: ( countable ) A sovereign state with dominant status on the globe and a very advanced military , especially the United States or formerly the Soviet Union .
secondary_definitions: ( countable , originally fiction ) An extraordinary physical or mental ability, especially possessed by a superhero or supervillain .
( obsolete , uncountable ) Electricity generated in a large plant that is tied into a regional network, on a larger scale than was common in the early years of commercial electricity production.
